                <head>21. Editorial Note</head>
                <p>On March 20, Ambassador <persName corresp="#p_DCD1">Dillon</persName> gave a
                    major speech to the Diplomatic Press Association of Paris on United States
                    policy toward French North Africa. The text of his speech is printed in
                    Department of State <hi rend="italic">Bulletin</hi>, April 2, 1956, pages
                    553–555.</p>
            </div>
